#To select charged residues in pymol
>select pos,(resn arg+lys+his)
>select neg ,(resn glu+asp)

#To move only one molecule in PyMOL
To do this, first choose Mouse > 3 Button Editing. 
Now hold down the Shift key and click anywhere on the desired molecule using the middle mouse button and drag to move it.
Only the selected molecule is moved and the rest remain as they are.
